Big Brother Naija, BBNaija Housemate, Kiddwaya has told his lover Erica that she can date Laycon. Recall that Laycon has shown his intention to have a relationship with Erica. However, the current BBNaija head of house chose to be with Kiddwaya but says she misses the friendship she has with Laycon. Speaking with Erica at the Head of House lounge, Kiddwaya said he would always offer her emotional support if she decides to date Laycon. “Whether we are in a relationship or flirting if it all stops I’m here for emotional support. “If you end up dating Laycon, I will still talk to you. “I’m not stubborn, I won’t withdraw, won’t watch you crumble or use my jealousy to make you suffer.”